            </li>
            {{/links}}

          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-3 vision-mission-container">
          <h4>Vision 2025</h4>
          <p>WA accelerates Bible translation around the world by empowering national translators and equipping the local church to translate God's Word into every language by 2025.</p>
